# Frontend Structure

## Directory Layout

```
apps/frontend/src/
  components/             # Shared components
    CmsManagement/        # CMS management interface
    Disclaimer/           # Disclaimer component
    InitProvider/         # App initialization provider
    Loading/              # Loading spinner component
    SiteHeader/           # Site header with search and nav
    ThemeProvider/        # Theme context provider
    ThemeSelector/        # Theme picker UI
    VodList/              # Video list grid
    VodPalyer/            # Video player (xgplayer)
    VodSearch/            # Video search with debounce
    VodSites/             # Video source selector
    VodTypes/             # Category type selector
  constant/               # Constants (llm.ts, site.ts, prompt.ts)
  hooks/                  # Custom hooks (useIsMobile)
  layouts/                # Layout components (BasicLayout)
  store/                  # Zustand stores
  themes/                 # Theme definitions (midnight, aurora, cyber)
  types/                  # TypeScript type definitions
  utils/                  # Utilities (HTTP request wrapper)
  pages/                  # React Router pages
    home/                 # Home page
    category/             # Category browsing
    detail/               # Video detail
    setting/              # Settings page
  services/               # API service layer
    index.ts              # Service exports
    vodhub/               # VodHub API calls
  data/                   # Static data
    builtin-cms.json      # Built-in video sources definition
  App.tsx                 # Application root component
  main.tsx                # Entry point
  globals.scss            # Global styles + CSS variables
```

## File Organization

### Pages
- Located in `pages/` using React Router
- Each page directory: `index.tsx` + optional `index.module.scss`
- Components are client-side by default (no `'use client'` directive needed)

### Components
- Located in `components/` directory
- Component directory format: `ComponentName/index.tsx` + `index.module.scss`
- Props interfaces exported with `export interface`

### State Management
- Located in `store/` directory
- File naming: `use{Name}Store.ts`
- Uses Zustand + `persist` middleware

### API Services
- Located in `services/` directory
- Organized by module (e.g., `vodhub/`)
- Uses generics for response types

### Styles
- SCSS Modules (`.module.scss`)
- Class names prefixed with `vod-next-` (historical naming convention)
- All colors use CSS variables from `globals.scss`

## Key File Locations
- Types: `types/index.ts`
- HTTP wrapper: `utils/request/index.ts`
- Theme config: `themes/index.ts`
- Theme Provider: `components/ThemeProvider/index.tsx`
- Theme store: `store/useThemeStore.ts`
- Video Sources store: `store/useVideoSourcesStore.ts`
- CMS Management component: `components/CmsManagement/index.tsx`
- Built-in CMS data: `src/data/builtin-cms.json`
